    "lyrics": {
      "text": "While Ga-bri-el was say-----ing Re-joice to thee,__ O Vir---gin, at his voice the Mas--ter__ of all___ things took__ flesh__ with---in__ thy___ pure_____ womb. He dwelt___ in thee as__ His ho-ly___ ark,__ as spake__ the__ right--eous__ Da--vid__ in__ the___ psalms.__ And in bear-------ing thy Cre-a----tor,__ thou___ wast__ shown___ forth___ more spa--cious__ than__ all___ the___ Heav-----ens. Glo--ry to Him that willed__ to dwell in___ thee.__ Glo--ry to Him____ that came forth__ from__ thee.__ Glo----ry to Him that, through thy bring-ing forth, hath__ de--liv-----ered____ us."
    }
